jangan beri mereka nama.

7
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,722
Mereka bukan lagi anak babi,
tapi makanan.

8
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:48,690
Aku hanya mengira sampai...

9
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:52,003
Baiklah.

10
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,328
Entah kenapa dengannya.

11
00:02:57,480 --> 00:03:00,942
Mungkin sakit,
mungkin bukan apa-apa.

12
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,717
Cepatlah sembuh, Violet.

13
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,747
Ayo, mari kita lakukan.

14
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,648
- Selamat pagi, Daryl.
